Parliament, Monday, 25 February 2018 – The Portfolio Committee on Justice and Correctional Services will tomorrow consider a draft report on the request to expedite procedures to remove the Public Protector from office. Details are as follows: 
	
	Date: Tuesday, 26 February 2019
	Time: 11:00
	Venue: Committee Room 1, Ground Floor, 120 Plein Street Building ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF THE PORTFOLIO COMMITTEE ON JUSTICE AND CORRECTIONAL SERVICES, MS MADIPOANE MOTHAPO. For media enquiries or interviews, please contact the committee’s Media Officer: Name: Rajaa Azzakani (Ms)
	Tel: 021 403 8437
	Cell: 081 703 9542
